Wed Apr 27 15:17:57 2005  John Ellis  <johne@verizon.net>

	* bar_info.c, bar_sort.c: Update for new pref_toolbar_button args.
	* fullscreen.c, layout.c: Remove use of GDK_HINT_USER_SIZE as we
